.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, december, may, august, november
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, quad-bike, subway, tram, snowmobile
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, hiking, video-games, camping, writing
House: art-deco, craftsman, modern, tower, townhouse

1. the english is the person who's birthday is in june
2. the spanish is the art-deco house
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's birthday is in december
4. the ukranian is the person who's hobby is hiking
5. the person who's birthday is in december is to the right of the person who's birthday is in may
6. the person driving the train is the townhouse house
7. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's birthday is in august
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the craftsman house
11. the person driving the quad-bike is to the left or right of the tower house
12. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is camping
13. the japanese is the person driving the snowmobile
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Birthday		|    august	|      november	|      june	|     may	|     december	|
| Hobby	|     writing	|      hiking	|      video-games	| camping	|     baking	|
| Transport		|     quad-bike	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| tram	|   parliament	|
| House		|     craftsman	|     tower	|     townhouse	|     art-deco	|     modern	|
